ref: Apollo has been the company's majority shareholder following an $850 million deal in 2007.

src: Paras on Lasse Virénin kaatumiskuva Münchenin olympialaisista.
mt: The best is Lasse Virénin kaatumiskuva the Munich Olympics.
ref: The best is the photo of Lasse Virén falling at the Munich Olympic Games.

src: Ich glaube, du hast etwas weitaus weniger lebensbedrohliches.
mt: I believe that you have something far less lebensbedrohliches.
ref: I think you have something a lot less life threatening.

src: Příště se Honza vrátí k pentatonice a zkusíte si ji dát dohromady právě s dvanáctkou.
mt: Next time, Honza will return to the pentatonice and try to put it together with the the.
ref: Then Honza returns to the pentatonic, and you can try to put it together with the twelve-member group.

src: "То, что Кэтрин Эштон встретилась тет-а-тет с Лукашенко, дает основания полагать, что отношения с ЕС будут размораживаться и дальше", - сказал он "Огоньку".
mt: "The fact that Catherine Ashton met tete-a-tete with Lukashenko, suggests that relations with the EU will be released in the future," he said "the Spark".
ref: “The fact that Catherine Ashton met face-to-face with Lukashenko gives one a basis to assume that relations with the EU will continue to thaw”, he told Ogonyok.

src: Vankilatyöntekijöiden järjestön ja oikeusministeriön edustajien tapaamisesta huolimatta asiasta ei syntynyt sopimusta, Bulgarian kansallinen radio (BNR) kertoo.
mt: Prison workers organisations and representatives of the Ministry of Justice, despite meeting with no agreement, the Bulgarian National Radio (b,) says.
ref: Despite the meetings between the prison officers union and the Justice Ministry representatives, an agreement was not reached, Bulgarian National Radio (BNR) informs.

src: Es gab mehrere Krebs-Flecken um meine Brust.
mt: There have been several cancer spots in my chest.
ref: There was multiple spotting [of cancer] around my chest.

src: Vor drei Monaten sah es so aus, als sei der Verkauf von Twitch an den Videodienst von Google für eine coole Milliarde beschlossene Sache, und die Zusammenarbeit erschien auch natürlich.
mt: Three months ago, it looked as the sale of twitch to the video service from Google for a cool billion done deal, and the cooperation appeared too of course.
ref: Three months ago the sale of Twitch to Google's video service, for a cool billion, looked all wrapped up, and the pairing seemed natural.

src: Siihen joukkoon kuuluivat toimittajat, pelaajien sukulaiset, suomalaiset koripallovalmentajat ja muutamat fanit.
mt: The group included journalists, Finnish basketball coaches, players' relatives and some fans.
ref: That number included journalists, players’ relatives, Finnish basketball coaches and some fans.

src: Ein Freibrief für alle komplizierten Details ist es aber nicht.
mt: A charter for all complicated details is it however not.
ref: However, there is still no charter explaining all the complex details.

src: Тем не менее, на заключительном брифинге Александр Лукашенко дал понять: все стороны не против, чтобы Минск остался центральной площадкой для встреч как в формате Россия--ОБСЕ--Украина, так и на уровне глав государств и высоких представителей Еврокомиссии.
mt: Nevertheless, at a final briefing Alexander Lukashenko let know: all parties not against that Minsk remained the central platform for meetings as in a format Russia - OSCE - Ukraine, and at the level of heads of states and high European Commission representatives.
ref: Nevertheless, in the final briefing, Aleksandr Lukashenko made it clear that all sides are not opposed to having Minsk remain as the main forum for meetings in the Russia-OSCE-Ukraine format, as well as for meetings between heads of state and EU high commissioners.

src: В Госдуму внесен проект закона, предусматривающий перенос даты вступления в силу уже принятого закона о персональных данных россиян - с 1 сентября 2016 года на 1 января 2015 года.
mt: In the State Duma introduced a Bill moving the date of entry into force, had already adopted law on personal data of Russians from the January 1, 2015 year September 1, 2016.
ref: A bill, which seeks to change the date of the entry into force of the already approved law on the personal data of Russian citizens from September 1, 2016 to January 1, 2015, has been introduced in the State Duma.

src: Я не могла поверить в это.
mt: I couldn't believe it.
ref: I couldn't believe it.

src: Nebylo jasné, jestli chtěla ropuchu zachránit nebo jestli ji chtěla sežrat sama, ale to bylo nepodstatné.
mt: It was not clear whether she wanted to save the toad, or if she wanted to eat alone, but that was irrelevant.
ref: It was not clear whether she wanted to save the toad or if she herself wanted to eat it, but that's not what was important.

src: Von Seiten der Stadt wollte man sich bisher nicht zu dem Vorhaben äußern.
mt: Of sides of the city, one wanted to express himself not yet for intention.
ref: Meanwhile, the town council refused to comment.

src: Ein Berufungsgericht bestätigt die erste erfolgreiche Personenschadensersatzklage in Großbritannien wegen Kontakts mit Asbest.
mt: A court of appeal confirms the first successful people damage suit in Great Britain because of contact with asbestos.
ref: Court of Appeal confirms the first successful personal injury claim in Britain as a result of asbestos exposure.

src: Ich fürchte, dass ich nochmal operiert werden muss.
mt: I fear that I must be operated on again.
ref: I fear I may need more surgery.

src: Hän on kansainvälisestikin tunnettu kapellimestari ja sai Pro Finlandia -mitalin vuonna 2011.
mt: He is internationally known as a conductor and received the Pro Finlandia Medal in 2011.
ref: She is an internationally known conductor, and received the Pro Finlandia Medal in 2011.

src: Автономия, которую российские дипломаты обсуждали на международных форумах дала бы региональным правительствам в Украине власть самим определять торговые соглашения и внешнюю политику, по сути дела, передавая Кремлю фактический контроль над территорией, которая бы соединила основную территорию России с Крымом.
mt: Autonomy, which Russian diplomats discussed at international forums would give regional governments in Ukraine, the authorities themselves define trade agreements and foreign policy, essentially, handing de facto control over the territory, which would have combined the main territory of Russia with Crimea.
ref: The autonomy that Russian diplomats have discussed in international forums would grant regional governments in Ukraine the authority to determine their own trade agreements and foreign relations, effectively handing the Kremlin de facto control over territory that would link the Russian mainland with Crimea.

src: Tohle je mnohem větší a také je tu mnohem víc plynů," říká vulkanolog Ármann Höskuldsson.
mt: This is much larger and there is also a lot more gas," says vulkanolog Ármann Höskuldsson.
ref: "This one is much larger, and there are also a lot more gases," says volcano expert Ármann Höskuldsson.

src: Die Techniker waren nicht in der Lage, einen halbwegs vernünftigen Sound zu schaffen.
mt: The technicians were not in a position to create a fairly reasonable sound.
ref: The engineers could not get a half-decent sound out of it.
